title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 3 categories of Health Segment on the x axis representing 5 groups: 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018.
Averaging these 5 groups, the highest category is found for Health Segment Healthcare with a mean value of 6731.0.
Followed by Life Science with a mean value of 4752.6.
The lowest category is observed at Performance Materials that has a mean value of 2395.8
showing a difference of 95.0% with the maximum value.

In case of Healthcare, 2014 shows more dominance than any other Health Segment and it has the lowest value in Performance Materials. On the other hand, group 2015 is the second impactful group in this chart, and it's highest in case of Healthcare and has the minimum dominance for Health Segment Performance Materials.
